at a time of 3 million unemployment<br />
and an insane government saying such jobs would be &quot;picked up&quot;...Earth to inbred fuck scum in Parliament!, jobs are going to decrease MASSIVELY in next few years regardless of financial issues, for example pal's job in warehouse was done away with as robots do it for no pay...<br />
We're in a global DPERESSION not recession and our government is slashing jobs and welfare...wow we know from history how THAT is gonna work out! <img src="images/smilies/rolleyes.gif" border="0" alt="" title="Roll Eyes (Sarcastic)" class="inlineimg" /><br />
