<a href="http://www.mirror.co.uk/news/uk-news/council-tax-huge-queues-outside-2033516" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">http://www.mirror.co.uk/news/uk-news...utside-2033516</a><br />
<br />
<div class="bbcode_container">
	<div class="bbcode_quote">
